Interface BackTrackingSupport

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CodeHandler, JavaCodeHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CodeModelBase, JavaCodeHandlerDebugImpl, JavaCodeHandlerImpl, JavaCodeModel, JenaCodeModel, JStatistics.StatisticsJavaCodeHandler, SPARQLQuerableCodeModel, ValidatingCodeModel

    public interface BackTrackingSupport
    This class extends CodeHandler to provide a back tracing mechanism able to accept unresolved types and fix it in a second time.
